 5.596126760596988e-26, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian military and President Vladimir Putin have noted that Ukraine often uses these kinds of opportunities to improve its military capabilities, according to Kremlin spokesperson Dmitry Peskov.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9998407302046544, \"rank\": 0.00014767100063167087, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1793703231082992e-17, \"text\": \"Vladimir Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 3.745196738763143e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kremlin\", \"score\": 0.9917548516592624, \"rank\": 0.008313695997445329, \"text\": \"Kremlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kremlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kremlin\"}, {\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dmitry_Peskov\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dmitry Peskov\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dmitry_Peskov\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dmitry_Peskov\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hoever, Peskov did not offer any particular instances of this kind of behaviour.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There has been continuous fighting in Ukraine since the conflict's start on February 24, 2022, without a declared ceasefire.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 3.745196738763143e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peskov did not go as far as ruling out an Olympic truce, but said no one had yet made any official steps in that regard.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The front lines in Ukraine have not shifted dramatically since late 2022, but Russia has regained the initiative since capturing the town of Avdiivka in February.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 3.745196738763143e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999975766514, \"rank\": 1.8990503427060683e-09, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1040, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avdiivka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Avdiivka\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avdiivka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avdiivka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukrainian forces are running low on ammunition as military aid remains held up in the US Congress and President Volodymyr Zelenskiy has said Russia may launch a major offensive in late spring or summer.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999994129945566, \"rank\": 5.738371861167831e-07, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"score\": 0.999999387611939, \"rank\": 6.123885412078865e-07, \"text\": \"US Congress\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"score\": 0.999999387611939, \"rank\": 6.123885412078865e-07, \"text\": \"US Congress\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999975766514, \"rank\": 1.8990503427060683e-09, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his interview with French media, Macron said France would \\\"do everything\\\" to bring about a truce in the conflicts in Ukraine, Gaza and Sudan, and that he would engage Chinese President Xi Jinping on the issue.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.990818859773886, \"rank\": 0.006352861303766579, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.596126760596988e-26, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9891905303671905, \"rank\": 0.005465288887149517, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 3.745196738763143e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.8867510904953676, \"rank\": 0.1277121739120905, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999993991372762, \"rank\": 5.979365898713669e-07, \"text\": \"Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\"}, {\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.8418429826326784, \"rank\": 0.18786997175256434, \"text\": \"Chinese President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xi Jinping\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is an opportunity on which I will try to involve many of our partners.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chinese president is coming to Paris in a few weeks, I will ask him to help me,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1560, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.999999999199872, \"rank\": 8.000604754118038e-10, \"text\": \"Chinese president\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999920255505, \"rank\": 7.974352015441075e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peskov, in reply to a separate question about China, said Beijing's position on the Ukraine conflict was \\\"very balanced and constructive\\\".\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso